OL,5, It is not affordable or sustainable to 
OL,6, keep vaccinating everyone against      
OL,7, Covid-19 on the planet regularly, a UK 
OL,8, vaccine scientist says.                
OL,10,FProf Sir Andrew Pollard, who helped    
OL,11,Fdevelop the Oxford-AstraZeneca vaccine,
OL,12,Fsays the most at risk should be        
OL,13,Fidentified and prioritised instead.    
OL,15,FHe said the vaccine rollout had gone   
OL,16,F"extremely well" in the UK but was     
OL,17,F"falling way behind" globally.         
OL,19,FBooster jabs have been offered to all  
OL,20,Feligible adults in the UK.             
